  "instructions": [
    "Heat a large pot over medium heat and add the chopped onion, carrots, and celery.",
    "Cook the mirepoix base for 5 minutes, stirring occasionally, until the vegetables are tender.",
    "Add the cubed eggplant to the pot and cook for an additional 5 minutes, stirring occasionally.",
    "Pour in the vegetable broth, canned diced tomatoes, smoked paprika, salt, and black pepper, and stir to combine.",
    "Bring the stew to a boil, then reduce the heat to low and simmer for 20 minutes, stirring occasionally.",
    "Taste and adjust the seasoning as needed.",
    "Stir in the chopped fresh parsley.",
    "Serve the stew hot, garnished with additional parsley if desired."
  ],
